> "It's time to reprogram this bot loyal to me"said Hydras while he 
> started to reprogram the pod as Predacon and programing an 
> abosloting loyalti to Hydras

She watched. Curiously, patiently.. her optics jumping continuously from the 
bot to Hydras.  He obviously had that ingenius mind that Megatron had. The 
more & more she was around him, the more she saw Megatron in him. So far, she 
hadn't seen much of Galvatron.. which was a good thing, in her opinion.
